Everything else in this repository (documentation, site, metadata) is MIT
unless a directory states otherwise.

In short: the mobile app is permissively licensed; the sync server and the
WhatsApp bridge are AGPL — you can self-host them freely, and if you offer a
modified version as a network service you must publish your changes.
